Rating: 4
So easy to prepare, so different, so economical, and so tasty. These were indeed exceptional. I baked them at 400 for 18 min or so and used raw shrimp. This method reduces fat and does not require tending. One third recipe made 4 shrimp cakes about 3 1/2 inches in diameter and half an inch thick. This is a great do ahead. Bake them while you are eating the first course. Shrimp cakes will be a repeat at our house.

