Rating: 4
These are outstanding! I used turkey kielbasa in place of the andouille sausage. I did not decrease the breadcrumbs or add egg--there was plenty of mayo to bind. I may reduce the mayo next time. I made a caynne aioli to go with: 2/3 c. mayo, 3/4 tsp. lemon juice, 1 pressed garlic clove, 1/2 tsp. cayenne and 1/4 tsp. dijon mustard. Combine in a small bowl with a whisk and refrigerate.

